@wheelers &amp; Froggy,<br/>
I believe one result was that TV networks called it for Reagan before West-coast polls had closed, causing some people to go home rather than vote. This is said to have affected some down-ballot races in California.<br/>
After this election, they changed their procedures, so that now they don't "call" the election for one or the other until West-coast polls have closed.
